Summary: flew overhead without a sound,lit up,big,odd,quick,solid,reflective,very shiny,turned abruptly
divs: Sighting Detailssitting on my back porch that faces south,screened in,porch light on, no other lights on.Two other people with me,having a cigarette,we all watched it fly over heading towards orlando international airport and we noticed it's odd design,lights,reflectiveness,and thought that it was an odd plane then we realised there was no sound and right at that time it turned and headed east.It didn't bank it turned.Good distance away at that point from my house, a little shy of where airplanes disappear over the horizon on way to airport.I don't know how high it was, not very, cause we could see the surface the lights were reflecting off.It had multicolored lights,in an odd pattern we all came up with nine lights on the object,u- shaped is how we described it.After it turned it had more of a triangle shape but extended,like the nose was very long in the front.(just lights at that point)very big to be able to see it that clearly,very flashy strobes on it as well,different than regular strobes on aircraft,very different.we were very excited to see a ufo,I knew we had to write it down as soon as we saw it while it was fresh in our minds.Sorry it took so long to report it.
